# Google Drive Integration via Google Apps Script
# No API keys or OAuth setup required!
#
# Steps:
# 1. Go to https://script.google.com → New project
# 2. Paste the Apps Script code (shown inside the app's "ربط بجوجل درايف" dialog)
# 3. Deploy as Web App: Execute as "Me", Access "Anyone"
# 4. Copy the deployment URL into the app's setup dialog
#
# No environment variables needed — the script URL is stored in the browser.
